<title>I REMEMBER EDEN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Eden ah lungthim hezing in,
 I Pathien batna a beitai;
 I Lallukhuk a kie'i,
 Kalvari thahat na vangin;
 Ka chang kittai ka Lallukhuk,
 Zie hi ka kipak hi.

[V2]
 2. Kalvari achun zie ni khan,
 Ka henbul chu a sattha tai;
 A hinna chu ei pie'i,
 Ka gitloh man ei dit zawh sak!
 Van lehkhabu ah A thaimang,
 Ei beng kitta puona.
 Hukdamna

[V3]
 3. Ginna'n va entie' mun leh thing,
 Isu tang chunga A thihna;
 Kumkhuo'n A hih hawih kha,
 Setan in eizo a mihing;
 Pathien mihinga hung suokin,
 Ei zawh sak, pakcha'i tiu.</lyrics>
</song>